7
00:00:10,660 --> 00:00:12,160
This has never happened before.

8
00:00:12,370 --> 00:00:15,200
- Can I help you?
- I'm here to see a patient.

9
00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:17,250
Annie, I'm Paul Spector.

10
