Where's the peck of pickled
peppers Peter Piper picked?

11
00:00:21,610 --> 00:00:24,310
- Did you learn that at school?
- No. From Peter Piper,

12
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,920
Mummy's friend.

13
00:00:25,980 --> 00:00:28,150
I warned you once before,
this is your last warning.

14
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:29,460
Good.

15
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,690
<i>They've managed to lift a partial
print from the scissors.</i>

16
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:33,790
<i>We've run it through the system
and found a match.</i>

17
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:35,230
Paul Spector.

18
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:37,040
<i>What have you done
with Rose Stagg?</i>

19
00:00:37,050 --> 00:00:40,110
Stella, I don't know what's going
to happen to me, to you,

20
00:00:40,120 --> 00:00:41,570
to anyone else in this world.

21
